title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - New update available - 1.29.30.0
description:
In this video we will go through the latest release notes as well as have a peak on the changes in the latest release of MSFS 2020. This update was specifically released to fix issues with the A310 but also some general fixes are included according to the release notes. Besides fixes there is also some new functionality added the EFB of the A310. We will first go through the release notes and then jump in the cockpit of the A310/
